1. GRANT OF LICENSE

   AI Plus Automation grants you a non-exclusive, non-transferable license
   to install and use the Software on your devices, subject to the terms
   of the plan you have purchased:

   a) FREE TIER: You may use the Software with the features available in
      the free tier at no cost, for personal or commercial use. The free
      tier includes all local memory operations (ingestion, recall, search,
      deletion, maintenance) across all interfaces (desktop app, CLI, MCP
      server, REST API). Free tier features are available indefinitely with
      no time limits or artificial restrictions.

   b) PRO LICENSE (Monthly): You may use the Software with all Pro features
      for the duration of your active subscription. Pro features include
      cross-device sync. If your subscription lapses or is cancelled,
      access to Pro features will revert to the free tier. All locally
      stored data remains accessible.

   c) PRO LICENSE (Lifetime): You may use the Software with all Pro features
      indefinitely for the lifetime of the product. "Lifetime" means the
      lifetime of the Software product, not the lifetime of the licensee.

   d) TRIAL: On first installation, a 14-day trial of Pro features is
      provided at no cost. After the trial period, access to Pro features
      reverts to the free tier unless a Pro license is purchased.

2. RESTRICTIONS

   You may NOT:
