   c) Rent, lease, lend, sell, or sublicense the Software;
   d) Remove or alter any proprietary notices, labels, or marks;
   e) Use the Software to develop a competing product or service;
   f) Share, transfer, or redistribute your license key to any third party.

3. DATA AND PRIVACY

   a) The Software stores all data locally on your device in a SQLite
      database. Your data is not uploaded to any cloud service unless you
      enable cross-device sync (Pro feature).
   b) When cross-device sync is enabled, your data is encrypted on your
      device using AES-256-GCM before transmission. The sync relay server
      stores and forwards only encrypted data and cannot read your memories.
   c) License validation requires periodic communication with our servers
      to verify your license status. No personal data beyond the license
      key is transmitted during this process.

